De Marijuan Bust.

Story
-------
The ct's have tracked down
the terrorist's Weedhouse.
But these are stoner ct's
and they have stolen a truck
and 3 Jack Flash weed plants.
So the terrorist's are well
pissed off and need to blow
up the van before the stoner
ct's can escape and get high!

Map remade by Robtronic.

Map was made using Monttinens
version of cs_crackhouse.

64 Spawn Points.

Custom models credits:
Shiroko: Weed plants.
Monttinen: Ghetto blaster.
